    <item>
      <title>en</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/purANam_vaiShNavam/kAvyam/padyam/shrIvaiShNava-kRtam/kAnchI-pUrNaH/devarAjAShTakam/en/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/purANam_vaiShNavam/kAvyam/padyam/shrIvaiShNava-kRtam/kAnchI-pUrNaH/devarAjAShTakam/en/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Source: &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2015/12/sri-dhevaraja-ashtakam/&#34;&gt;TW&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;SrI:&lt;br&gt;&#xA;SrImathE SatakOpAya nama:&lt;br&gt;&#xA;SrImathE rAmAnujAya nama:&lt;br&gt;&#xA;SrImath varavaramunayE nama:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/dhevaperumal-nachiyars-perundhevi-thayar-e1449467380568.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;figure class=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/dhevaperumal-nachiyars-perundhevi-thayar-e1449467380568.jpg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/dhevaperumal-nachiyars-perundhevi-thayar-e1449467380568.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;dhevaperumal-nachiyars-perundhevi-thayar&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/sri-mahalakshmi/&#34;&gt;perundhEvith thAyAr&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/sriman-narayanan/&#34;&gt;varadharAja perumAL&lt;/a&gt; with ubhaya nAchchiyArs – kAnchIpuram&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/thirukkachi-nambi-kanchi.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;figure class=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/thirukkachi-nambi-kanchi.jpg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/thirukkachi-nambi-kanchi.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;thirukkachi-nambi-kanchi&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/thirukkachi-nambi/&#34;&gt;thirukkachchi nambi&lt;/a&gt; – kAnchIpuram&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;audiohttpsdivyaprabandhamkoyilorgindexphp201512sri-dhevaraja-ashtakam-audio&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2015/12/sri-dhevaraja-ashtakam-audio/&#34;&gt;Audio&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;e-book: &lt;a href=&#34;http://1drv.ms/1JARZeX&#34;&gt;http://1drv.ms/1JARZeX&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/thirukkachi-nambi/&#34;&gt;thirukkachchi nambi&lt;/a&gt; have mercifully written a beautiful samskritha sthOthra prabandham named SrI dhEvarAja ashtakam (8 SlOkams) which brings out the glories of &lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/sriman-narayanan/&#34;&gt;dhEvap perumAL (SrI varadharAja)&lt;/a&gt; who is the divine consort of &lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/sri-mahalakshmi/&#34;&gt;perundhEvith thAyAr&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;nyAya vEdhAntha vidhvAn dhAmal vangIpuram srI u vE pArthasArathy aiyengAr swamy has written a simple thamizh translation for this wonderful prabandham. We will see the English translation of the same here.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>hi</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/purANam_vaiShNavam/kAvyam/padyam/shrIvaiShNava-kRtam/kAnchI-pUrNaH/devarAjAShTakam/hi/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/purANam_vaiShNavam/kAvyam/padyam/shrIvaiShNava-kRtam/kAnchI-pUrNaH/devarAjAShTakam/hi/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Source: &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2016/01/sri-dhevaraja-ashtakam-hindi/&#34;&gt;TW&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;श्री-&lt;br&gt;&#xA;श्रीमते शठकोपाये नम-&lt;br&gt;&#xA;श्रीमते रामानुजाये नम-&lt;br&gt;&#xA;श्रीमद्वरवरमुनये नम-&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://srivaishnavagranthamshindi.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/1-dhevaperumal-nachiyars-perundhevi-thayar-e1449467380568.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;figure class=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://srivaishnavagranthamshindi.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/1-dhevaperumal-nachiyars-perundhevi-thayar-e1449467380568.jpg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://srivaishnavagranthamshindi.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/1-dhevaperumal-nachiyars-perundhevi-thayar-e1449467380568.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;1.dhevaperumal-nachiyars-perundhevi-thayar-e1449467380568&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://guruparamparaihindi.wordpress.com/2013/08/31/dhivya-dhampati/&#34;&gt;पेरुन्देवित् तायार,&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://guruparamparaihindi.wordpress.com/2013/08/31/dhivya-dhampati/&#34;&gt;देव पेरुमाल (श्रीवरदराज भगवान)&lt;/a&gt;उभयनाच्चियार के साथ – कांचीपुरम&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://srivaishnavagranthamshindi.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/2-thirukkachi-nambi-kanchi.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;figure class=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://srivaishnavagranthamshindi.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/2-thirukkachi-nambi-kanchi.jpg?w=200&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://srivaishnavagranthamshindi.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/2-thirukkachi-nambi-kanchi.jpg?w=200&#34; alt=&#34;2.thirukkachi-nambi-kanchi&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://guruparamparaihindi.wordpress.com/2014/03/09/thirukkachi-nambi/&#34;&gt;श्री कांचिपूर्ण स्वामीजी&lt;/a&gt;– कांचीपुरम&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;audiohttpsdivyaprabandhamkoyilorgindexphp201512sri-dhevaraja-ashtakam-audio&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2015/12/sri-dhevaraja-ashtakam-audio/&#34;&gt;Audio&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;e-book: &lt;a href=&#34;http://1drv.ms/1ZV4dqh&#34;&gt;http://1drv.ms/1ZV4dqh&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://guruparamparaihindi.wordpress.com/2014/03/09/thirukkachi-nambi/&#34;&gt;श्री कांचिपूर्ण स्वामीजी&lt;/a&gt; ने कृपा करके श्री देवराज अष्टकम् (8 श्लोक) नामक एक सुंदर संस्कृत स्तोत्र प्रबंध की रचना की जो &lt;a href=&#34;https://guruparamparaihindi.wordpress.com/2013/08/31/dhivya-dhampati/&#34;&gt;पेरुन्देवित् तायार&lt;/a&gt; के स्वामी &lt;a href=&#34;https://guruparamparaihindi.wordpress.com/2013/08/31/dhivya-dhampati/&#34;&gt;देव पेरुमाल (श्रीवरदराज भगवान)&lt;/a&gt; की महिमा का गान करता है।&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;न्याय वेदांत विद्वान् दामल वन्गिपुरम श्री ऊ.वे. पार्थसारथी ऐयेंगार स्वामी ने इस अद्भुत प्रबंध का अनुवाद सरल और सुगम तमिल भाषा में किया है। हम यहाँ उसके हिंदी अनुवाद को देखेंगे।&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ta</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/purANam_vaiShNavam/kAvyam/padyam/shrIvaiShNava-kRtam/kAnchI-pUrNaH/devarAjAShTakam/ta/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/purANam_vaiShNavam/kAvyam/padyam/shrIvaiShNava-kRtam/kAnchI-pUrNaH/devarAjAShTakam/ta/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Source: &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2015/12/sri-dhevaraja-ashtakam-tamil/&#34;&gt;TW&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;श्री:&lt;br&gt;&#xA;श्रीमदे सडगोबाय नम:&lt;br&gt;&#xA;श्रीमदे रामानुजाय नम:&lt;br&gt;&#xA;श्रीमत् वरवरमुनये नम:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/dhevaperumal-nachiyars-perundhevi-thayar-e1449467380568.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;figure class=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/dhevaperumal-nachiyars-perundhevi-thayar-e1449467380568.jpg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/dhevaperumal-nachiyars-perundhevi-thayar-e1449467380568.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/sri-mahalakshmi/&#34;&gt;pèrundevit तायार्&lt;/a&gt;, उबय नाच्चियार्गळुडऩ् &lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/sriman-narayanan/&#34;&gt;वरदराजप् पॆरुमाळ्&lt;/a&gt; – काञ्जीबुरम्&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/thirukkachi-nambi-kanchi.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;figure class=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/thirukkachi-nambi-kanchi.jpg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/thirukkachi-nambi-kanchi.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;thirukkachi-nambi-kanchi&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/thirukkachi-nambi/&#34;&gt;tirukkacci नम्बि&lt;/a&gt; – काञ्जीबुरम्&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;audiohttpsdivyaprabandhamkoyilorgindexphp201512sri-dhevaraja-ashtakam-audio&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2015/12/sri-dhevaraja-ashtakam-audio/&#34;&gt;Audio&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;e-book: &lt;a href=&#34;http://1drv.ms/1TLbwK1&#34;&gt;http://1drv.ms/1TLbwK1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/thirukkachi-nambi/&#34;&gt;तिरुक्कच्चि नम्बिगळ्&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/sri-mahalakshmi/&#34;&gt;पॆरुन्देवित् तायारिऩ्&lt;/a&gt; प्रिय केळ्वऩाऩ&lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/sriman-narayanan/&#34;&gt;वरदराजप् पॆरुमाळिऩ्&lt;/a&gt; पॆरुमैयै वॆळिप्पडुत्तुम् नोक्कुडऩ् श्री तेवराज अष्टगम् ऎऩ्ऩुम् अऴगिय संस्क्रुद स्तोत्र प्रबन्दत्तै अरुळिच्चॆय्दु उळ्ळार्।&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;न्याय वेदान्द वित्वाऩ् तामल् वङ्गीबुरम् श्री उ वे पार्त्तसारदि ऐयङ्गार् स्वामि इन्दप् प्रबन्दत्तिऱ्कुत् तमिऴिल् ऒरु ऎळिय पॊऴिप्पुरै अरुळियुळ्ळार्। अदै इङ्गे नाम् काण्बोम्।&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;पिऩ्वरुम् कट्टुरैगळिल् इन्द प्रबन्दत्तै अनुबविप्पोम्:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>te</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/purANam_vaiShNavam/kAvyam/padyam/shrIvaiShNava-kRtam/kAnchI-pUrNaH/devarAjAShTakam/te/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/purANam_vaiShNavam/kAvyam/padyam/shrIvaiShNava-kRtam/kAnchI-pUrNaH/devarAjAShTakam/te/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Source: &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2015/12/sri-dhevaraja-ashtakam-telugu/&#34;&gt;TW&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;श्री-&lt;br&gt;&#xA;श्रीमते शठकोपाय नम-&lt;br&gt;&#xA;श्रीमते रामानुजाय नम-&lt;br&gt;&#xA;श्रीमद्वरवरमुनये नम-&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/dhevaperumal-nachiyars-perundhevi-thayar-e1449467380568.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;figure class=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/dhevaperumal-nachiyars-perundhevi-thayar-e1449467380568.jpg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/dhevaperumal-nachiyars-perundhevi-thayar-e1449467380568.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;dhevaperumal-nachiyars-perundhevi-thayar&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://guruparamparaitelugu.wordpress.com/2013/09/04/divya-dhampathi/&#34;&gt;श्री पॆरुंदेवि तायर् , श्री भु समेत वरदराज (पॆररुळालन्) पॆरुमाळ्&lt;/a&gt;, कंचिपुरम्&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/thirukkachi-nambi-kanchi.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;figure class=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/thirukkachi-nambi-kanchi.jpg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/thirukkachi-nambi-kanchi.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;thirukkachi-nambi-kanchi&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://guruparamparaitelugu.wordpress.com/2014/03/19/thirukkachi-nambi/&#34;&gt;तिरुक्कच्चि नंबि&lt;/a&gt; – कंचिपुरम्&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;audiohttpsdivyaprabandhamkoyilorgindexphp201512sri-dhevaraja-ashtakam-audio&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2015/12/sri-dhevaraja-ashtakam-audio/&#34;&gt;Audio&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://guruparamparaitelugu.wordpress.com/2014/03/19/thirukkachi-nambi/&#34;&gt;श्री तिरुक्कच्चि नंबि&lt;/a&gt; स्वामि अनुग्रहिंचिन देवराजाष्टकम् अने 8 श्लोकमुलुगल ई दिव्य काव्यम् लो श्री कंचि महालक्ष्मि पॆरुंदेवि तायर् पतियगु श्री देवराज {वरदराज} पॆरुमाळ् वैभवमुनु लोकान चाटुचुन्नारु.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;न्याय विद्वान् दामल् वन्गीपुरम् श्री उ.वे.पार्थसारति ऐय्यंगार् ई प्रबंधमुनकु सरलमगु तमिळ अनुवादमुनु चेसिनारु, ई अनुवादमुनकु तॆलुगुलो प्रतिअनुवादमुनु इक्कड चूडवच्चुनु.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
